SUPPORTERAPISCHEMA.json
A clean, future‑proof schema for programmatic sponsor ingestion.

`json
{
  "type": "object",
  "title": "Supporter",
  "properties": {
    "id": { "type": "string" },
    "name": { "type": "string" },
    "tier": {
      "type": "string",
      "enum": [
        "community",
        "developer",
        "infrastructure",
        "ecosystem",
        "institutional"
      ]
    },
    "joined_at": { "type": "string", "format": "date-time" },
    "link": { "type": "string", "format": "uri" },
    "avatar_url": { "type": "string", "format": "uri" },
    "message": { "type": "string" }
  },
  "required": ["id", "name", "tier", "joined_at"]
}
`

This schema is intentionally minimal, extensible, and GitDigital‑aligned.